ics and forgotten places. Together, they look to leave a legacy in their wake\n<br><br>\nYet, their journey begins in blood and tragedy.\n<br><br>\nYour choices are everything and they can reshape your life in this place, even the world around you.  Will you become strong enough to survive the journey and reach the end? Will you find the power to change this grim reflection of our own world? Will your legacy be one of peace and honor, or stained by bloodshed and destruction?\n<br><br>\nWhen you look in the mirror at the end, what reflection will you see there?<h4>Features</h4><br><ul class="bb_ul"><li> Non-linear RPG with real time combat (with slow or pause) where tactics and party power are equally important.\n<br></li><li> Player choices impact the world: it can be destroyed or saved, and the stories that unfold will lead to multiple endings reflecting the characters personalities and decisions. \n<br></li><li> 4 base classes / 16 specialization classes to discover - with the ability to mix skill trees - including some rare classes which can only be found in remote locations or through chained quests.\n<br></li><li> New RPG system, promoting experimentation and requiring frequent adaptation to the new challenges.\n<br></li><li> 4K Graphics, Free movement camera, Multiple enviro biomes, Visually Striking VFX, Cutscenes (in-game and animated illustrations), Animations created with in-house MOCAP, Great Soundtrack, Character Customization, Day/Night cycle, Crafting, Enchanting, Research\n<br></li><li> High-replayability factor due to large pool of quests, local, and world events. One cannot uncover all of the content in a single playthrough. </li></ul><br><img src="https://items.gog.com/dark_envoy/1_-_World_Map_550.jpg" style="margin: auto;display:block;width: 600px"><p class="description__copyrights">\n             Copyright 2019 | Event Horizon Ltd. | All rights reserved\n        </p>	518.39	1969-12-31	BR0	2021-01-31 20:38:33.894+00	\N	\N	2021-01-31 20:38:35.215+0